def Sender():
    return ui.setRefractionManual
app.sender = Sender
app.refractionSource = 'onlineWeather'
app.deviceStat['mount'] = True
with mock.patch.object(app, 'movingAverageRefractionParameters',
    return_value=(10, 10)):
    with mock.patch.object(app.app.mount.setting, 'setRefractionParam',
        return_value=True):
        suc = app.updateRefractionParameters()
        assert suc
